description:
Notes
So I'm trying to go through and get every episode of Stossel released. This was one of the specials that hadn't been posted on here. It's his first special, from 2010. The quality is mediocre, but totally watchable. I had to dig it out of some random tube site and stitch it together. Check the screenshots & encode info at the bottom.

There are currently 2 episodes of Stossel which I can not find anywhere online. If anyone has any leads on these episodes, or could upload them, I'd be extreme grateful. Here are the two episodes.

Show Information
John F. Stossel is an American consumer reporter, investigative journalist, author, libertarian columnist, and former co-anchor for the ABC News show 20/20. In this show he looks at consumer-focused topics, such as civil liberties, the business of health care, and free trade.
